Type: Package
Package: MinirhizotronR
Title: Extracting Depth Resolved Metrics from Minirhizotron Root Scans
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Johannes",
             family = "Cunow",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "johannes.cunow@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4830-1162")))
Maintainer: Johannes Cunow <johannes.cunow@gmail.com>
Description: With MinirhizotronR, analyzing root scans from minirhizotron
    tubes becomes a piece of cake. It enables the user to extract various
    root metrics and relate them to a depth distribution, or assess
    rotational biases. It relies on outside handling of Image
    Segmentation.
